data.title: Missy Elliott ~ Songs List
data.text:
Spin: "...Ridiculously, abstrusely , hyper-generously funky....It's both consistently catchy and consistently weird in all the right ways..." - Grade: A-

Rolling Stone: 3.5 stars out of 5 -- "She re-teams with Timbaland for the superbly titled 'DripDemeanor,' an R&B slow jam....It's a vital reminder of why we've been missing her so much."

2.Cool Off

3.DripDemeanor
